NAME="image"
SECTION="group"
SUMMARY="Container image command group"
USAGE="singularity [...] image.<command> [...] <image path>"

print_help() {
cat<<EOF

This is a command group that supports the management of various container
image functions.

IMAGE GROUP COMMANDS:

    image.create    Create an image
    image.import    Import data into an image
    image.expand    Expand an image
    image.export    Export the contents of an image

All group commands have their own help output:

    $ singularity help image.create
    $ singularity image.create --help

For additional help, please visit our public documentation pages which are
found at:

    https://www.sylabs.io/docs/
EOF
}
